<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background: #f0f4ff;
        color: #2b5cff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: inline-block;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Email Verification</h2>
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Your OTP (One-Time Password) for verification is:</p>
      <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>
      <p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>— SwiftShip Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
